<div id="homemaintext">
<h1 style="padding: 15px 0px 15px 0px; font-size: 26px;">What is Spellzone?</h1>
<p>Spellzone unlocks the mystery of American English spelling. Adapting to all abilities, it enables students, including SEND, SLD and ESL, to study independently on any platform in school, at home or on the go. Dynamic reporting tools provide teachers with time-saving monitoring and evaluation of all student activity and results.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="homegreeninner">
<h2 style="padding: 10px 0px 15px 0px; font-size: 26px;">How does Spellzone work?</h2>
<div id="homewhat1">
<h3>Spelling Ability Test</h3>
<p>Assesses prior knowledge<br />
Creates individual course pathways<br />
Automatic re-testing</p>
</div>
<div id="homewhat2">
<h3>Spelling Course</h3>
<p>Based on phonic progression<br />
Covers all English spelling rules<br />
Multi-sensory activites and tests</p>
</div>
<div id="homewhat3">
<h3>Word Lists</h3>
<p>
Course, curriculum and grade lists
<br />
1000s of pre-loaded lists or create your own<br />
Use with activities, games and worksheets</p>
</div>
